{"type":"text","timestamp":1775848396198,"sessionID":"ses_28731db20ffeapDDhzVx7gaQDp","part":{"id":"prt_d78d00e49001Blcdr477POkp93","messageID":"msg_d78cffc75001E33hvu1Kyk4ues","sessionID":"ses_28731db20ffeapDDhzVx7gaQDp","type":"text","text":"Done. The delta-spec.md for AR-010 has been expanded from 3 scenarios to 27 comprehensive GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios covering:\n\n- Session Configuration (3 scenarios)\n- Session ID Generation (2 scenarios)\n- Session Storage (4 scenarios)\n- Session Middleware (4 scenarios)\n- Session Affinity/Sticky Sessions (3 scenarios)\n- Session Lifecycle - Expiration (2 scenarios)\n- Session Lifecycle - Cleanup (2 scenarios)\n- Session Cookie Configuration (3 scenarios)\n- Session Metrics (4 scenarios)\n- Graceful Shutdown (1 scenario)\n\nAll scenarios follow the OpenSpec format matching the style in AR-009.","time":{"start":1775848396197,"end":1775848396197}}}
